flowchart TD
    START[What is the primary workload?] --> DM{Workload type?}

    DM -->|Relational structured data| REL{Need full SQL Server instance features?}
    DM -->|NoSQL or globally distributed| NOSQL{Access pattern?}
    DM -->|Analytics OLAP or DW| AN{Analytics workload?}
    DM -->|Full-text or vector search| SEARCH[Azure AI Search]
    DM -->|IoT or edge-constrained device| EDGE[Azure SQL Edge]
    DM -->|Caching or session state| CACHE[Azure Cache for Redis]

    REL -->|Yes - SQL Agent, CLR, VNet, linked servers| CTRL{Need OS-level control?}
    REL -->|No - cloud-native or open-source| NEW{Engine preference?}

    CTRL -->|Yes| SQLVM[SQL Server on Azure VM]
    CTRL -->|No| SQLMI[Azure SQL Managed Instance]

    NEW -->|Microsoft SQL engine| SQLSIZE{DB exceeds 4 TB?}
    NEW -->|PostgreSQL| PG[Azure DB for PostgreSQL Flexible Server]
    NEW -->|MySQL or MariaDB| MYSQL[Azure DB for MySQL Flexible Server]

    SQLSIZE -->|Yes| HYPER[Azure SQL Database Hyperscale]
    SQLSIZE -->|No| SQLDB[Azure SQL Database]

    NOSQL -->|Document or JSON| COSMOSDOC[Cosmos DB - Core SQL or MongoDB API]
    NOSQL -->|Wide-column Cassandra-compatible| COSMOSCASS[Cosmos DB - Cassandra API]
    NOSQL -->|Graph traversal| COSMOSGRAPH[Cosmos DB - Gremlin API]
    NOSQL -->|Key-value| KV{Multi-region or high throughput?}

    KV -->|Yes| COSMOSTBL[Cosmos DB - Table API]
    KV -->|No| TBLS[Azure Table Storage]

    AN -->|T-SQL DW predictable queries| SYNDW[Synapse Dedicated SQL Pool]
    AN -->|Spark Delta Lake big data engineering| SYNSP[Synapse Spark Pool or Azure Databricks]
    AN -->|Real-time telemetry logs time-series| ADX[Azure Data Explorer]
    AN -->|Semantic layer BI tabular models| AAS[Azure Analysis Services]
